    • inputOrder

      public final String inputOrder
      String specifying the tensor type for each input. The ith character in this string specifies the type of the ith input, and is one of: 'R' (ragged), 'D' (dense), or 'S' (sparse). This attr is used to ensure that the crossed values are combined in the order of the inputs from the call to tf.ragged.cross.
